<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5014331>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15­19. Mecynostomella spinosa sp.n., male holotype. 15, genitalia, lateral view; 16, genitalia, dorsal view; 17, genitalia, ventral view; 18, phallus, lateral view; 19, phallus, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5014331/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5014329>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6­14. Mecynostomella species, right wings and wing details. 6, Mecynostomella spinosa sp.n. male, right wings and vein terminology; 7, Mecynostomella spinosa sp.n. male, scaloid seta from forewing Cu2, highly magnified; 8, Mecynostomella spinosa sp.n. female, right wings; 9, Mecynostomella brevis sp.n. male, right wings; 10, Mecynostomella hollowayi sp.n. male, right wings, a indicates the position of a pale area in the Cu­ and A­ area of the forewing, and made from minute structures shown in the next figure; 11, details of a single structure forming a pentagon and with a central opening, and which build up a pale area of the forewing as indicated in the previous figure; 12, Mecynostomella fusca Kimmins, 1953, right wings, with area covered by sensillae indicated by a surrounding black line; 13, Mecynostomella flinti sp.n., detail from wing membrane of dark area between forewing Cu and A, showing position of a modified sensilla and sensilla bases (t), dorsal view; 14, same species and sensilla, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5014329/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5014337>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23­27. Mecynostomella brevis sp.n., male holotype. 23, genitalia, lateral view; 24, genitalia, dorsal view; 25, genitalia, ventral view; 26, phallus, lateral view; 27, phallus, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5014337/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5014341>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28­32. Mecynostomella caledonia sp.n., male holotype. 28, genitalia, lateral view; 29, genitalia, dorsal view; 30, genitalia, ventral view; 31, phallus, lateral view; 32, phallus, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5014341/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5014353>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46­50. Mecynostomella flinti sp.n., male holotype. 46, genitalia, lateral view; 47, genitalia, dorsal view; 48, genitalia, ventral view; 49, phallus, lateral view; 50, phallus, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5014353/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5014351>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41­45. Mecynostomella sigma sp.n., male holotype. 41, genitalia, lateral view; 42, genitalia, dorsal view; 43, genitalia, ventral view; 44, phallus, lateral view; 45, phallus, ventral view." ;
